<br>
Ethereal parchments should be much more common. Folks just will not be able to advance too far in PoP without their spell upgrades, and at the very least we should have access to our basic spells sooner than we do now. Hell, I've seen more pieces of actual gear drop than parchments (in point of fact, I have seen zero parchments drop).  Wouldn't bug me much if the spectral and shadowy parchments were hard to get, especially on the first tier of planes. But Ethereal Parchments just shouldn't be as rare as they are now.<br>
